* Larry &quot;Madthrash&quot; Madison – guitars (1984–1987)
* Damien Matthews – bass (2010–2015)
* Iscariah – bass (2002–2010)
* Jared Faulk – bass (2001)
* Dustin Havnen – bass (1998–2001)
* Bill &quot;Blaster&quot; Bork – bass (1984–1987)
