<text>Albert Hornby is the name of:

*A. H. Hornby (1877–1952), English cricketer, son of A. N. Hornby
*A. N. Hornby (1847–1925), English rugby and cricket captain
*A. S. Hornby (1898–1978), English grammarian, lexicographer and researcher into second language teaching</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q18716168" start="32" end="44" title="A. H. Hornby" label="A. H. Hornby"/>
<link wikidata="Q2743474" start="98" end="110" title="A. N. Hornby" label="A. N. Hornby"/>
